Library API Version: 1
This is not a network API, rather this is a library API. 

API Specification: BankAPI

Endpoints:

  - version()
    Description: Return the version of this API.

  - create_account(owner)
    Description: Create a new account for the given owner.

  - deposit(account_id, amount)
    Description: Deposit money into the specified account.

  - withdraw(account_id, amount)
    Description: Withdraw money if balance allows.

  - balance(account_id)
    Description: Return current account balance.

  - transactions(account_id)
    Description: Return the transaction history.


